s"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%3A------------/" target="_blank">:</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Steve------------/" target="_blank">Steve</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Talley------------/" target="_blank">Talley</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-David------------/" target="_blank">David</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Ellison------------/" target="_blank">Ellison</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Dean------------/" target="_blank">Dean</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Cameron------------/" target="_blank">Cameron</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Christopher------------/" target="_blank">Christopher</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Showerman------------/" target="_blank">Showerman</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-K.T.------------/" target="_blank">K.T.</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Tatara------------/" target="_blank">Tatara</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Jerad------------/" target="_blank">Jerad</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Anderson------------/" target="_blank">Anderson</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Sandy------------/" target="_blank">Sandy</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Modic------------/" target="_blank">Modic</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Jossara------------/" target="_blank">Jossara</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Jinaro------------/" target="_blank">Jinaro</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Dean------------/" target="_blank">Dean</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Cain------------/" target="_blank">Cain</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----Drew--------/" target="_blank">Drew</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----Ann--------/" target="_blank">Ann</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----Rosenberg--------/" target="_blank">Rosenberg</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/20/" target="_blank">福利</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">美国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2010/" target="_blank">2010</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>Eric是一名天才过人的高尔夫球手，也是一个非常没有修养的大学生一次高尔夫对决中，他输给了一对整形外科医生，他的生活由此发生了翻天覆地的变化：他失去了钱，失去了女友，失去了尊严，失去了高尔夫球，他的坏男孩的生活态度戛然而止。Eric和好朋友Tyler打算找回自己的生活，成为一个真正的男子汉。</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/72983/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/72981/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-02-21/201902211550748099.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">1.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/72981/">美国派9:爱熟女</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-Joseph------------/" target="_blank">Joseph</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Booton------------/" target="_blank">Booton</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Ramon------------/" target="_blank">Ramon</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Camacho------------/" target="_blank">Camacho</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Philip------------/" target="_blank">Philip</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Marlatt------------/" target="_blank">Marlatt</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Jack------------/" target="_blank">Jack</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Cullison------------/" target="_blank">Cullison</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Jamie------------/" target="_blank">Jamie</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Bernadette------------/" target="_blank">Bernadette</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----Scott--------/" target="_blank">Scott</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----Wheeler--------/" target="_blank">Wheeler</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/20/" target="_blank">福利</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">美国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2010/" target="_blank">2010</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>《美国派9：我爱熟女》，是一部Scott Wheeler执导，Joseph Booton、Ramon Camacho、Philip Marlatt、Jack Cullison等主演的美国喜剧电影影片讲述一群大学生与熟女的情爱故事</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/72981/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/68108/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-01-27/201901271548585330.png"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">8.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/68108/">美国派7：索爱天书</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-Eugene------------/" target="_blank">Eugene</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Levy------------/" target="_blank">Levy</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Bug------------/" target="_blank">Bug</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Hall------------/" target="_blank">Hall</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Kevin------------/" target="_blank">Kevin</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-M.------------/" target="_blank">M.</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Horton------------/" target="_blank">Horton</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Brandon------------/" target="_blank">Brandon</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Hardesty------------/" target="_blank">Hardesty</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Beth------------/" target="_blank">Beth</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Behrs------------/" target="_blank">Behrs</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Melanie------------/" target="_blank">Melanie</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Papalia------------/" target="_blank">Papalia</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----John--------/" target="_blank">John</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----Putch--------/" target="_blank">Putch</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/7/" target="_blank">喜剧片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">美国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2009/" target="_blank">2009</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>　　距第一部美国派已有10年，三个没救的新处发现了藏在高中图书馆的“索爱天书”不过不幸的是，书已经残缺不全了。靠着书中不完整的建议，三人踏上了滑稽的破处之旅。</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-